  m_Name: 1_MAMA
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Game.Collectable.CollectableItem
  id: 1_MAMA
  headerName: "THE VIEW FROM MAMA\u2019S PORCH"
  content: "(A handwritten note tucked into a weathered recipe book)\n\n\nElias,
    if you\u2019re looking for the flour, I moved it to the tin under the sink. The
    humidity is getting to the paper bags. I spent the morning watching the hawks
    circle the Peak. There\u2019s three of them this year\u2014the parents and a
    little one. They look so small against the blue, but they own the whole world
    up here. Come by for tea when you\u2019re done with the traps. The mountain is
    so quiet today, it\u2019s like it\u2019s holding its breath just to hear us laugh.\n\n"
  type: 0
  icon: {fileID: 0}
  dialogData: {fileID: 0}
